sequenceDiagram
    participant Target as Service / Host
    participant Agent as Collector Agent
    participant Stream as Event Stream Buffer
    participant TSDB as TSDB (Hot/Warm/Cold)
    participant Eval as Alert Evaluator
    participant Router as Alert Router

    Note over Target,Agent: Scrape (pull) collection
    loop Every 10s
        Agent->>Target: GET /metrics
        Target-->>Agent: name + tags + value samples
        Agent->>Stream: Forward batch
    end

    Note over Stream,TSDB: Ingest path
    Stream->>TSDB: Write workers batch + Gorilla-compress
    alt Cardinality over budget
        TSDB-->>Stream: Reject series, page owning team
    else Within budget
        TSDB->>TSDB: Append to hot tier (SSD, 10s res)
    end

    Note over Eval,Router: Alert evaluation
    loop Every 30s
        Eval->>TSDB: Run rule query (PromQL)
        TSDB-->>Eval: Time series result
        alt Threshold breached for "for: 5m"
            Eval->>Router: Fire alert
            Router->>Router: Group, dedupe, apply silences, inhibit
            Router-)Target: Notify on-call (paging channel)
        end
    end

    Note over TSDB: Background downsample 10s -> 1min -> 1hr across tiers
